p.k: When Gumball rejects “The Rejects Club”, the rejects wreak their revenge. / Gumball and Darwin make their Dad believe in magic again. / Ms Simian sets out to “befriend” Gumball in order to win a Favourite Teacher Award. / Gumball and Darwin give Mr Robinson a home and end up saving his marriage. / Gumball and Darwin help Anais rescue her doll from Tina Rex.
